### ===========================
### KONSERTER
### ===========================

### Hent konserter
GET {{base}}/api/konserter

### Hent kommende konserter
GET {{base}}/api/konserter?upcoming=true&$top=5

### Opprett konsert
POST {{base}}/api/konserter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Varkonsert 2026",
  "date": "2026-04-18",
  "time": "19:00",
  "location": "Kulturhuset, Store sal",
  "address": "Youngstorget 3, Oslo",
  "description": "Var arlige varkonsert.",
  "ticketPrice": 250,
  "ticketsAvailable": 100,
  "isPublic": true
}

### Oppdater konsert (fyll inn ID)
PATCH {{base}}/api/konserter/FYLL-INN-ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Oppdatert konserttittel",
  "ticketsAvailable": 150
}

### Slett konsert (fyll inn ID)
DELETE {{base}}/api/konserter/FYLL-INN-ID

### Bestill billetter
POST {{base}}/api/konserter/billett
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "concertId": "FYLL-INN-KONSERT-ID",
  "name": "Ola Nordmann",
  "email": "ola@test.no",
  "ticketCount": 2,
  "totalPrice": 500
}

