### ===========================
### FILER
### ===========================

### Hent filer
GET {{base}}/api/filer

### Oppdater filmetadata
POST {{base}}/api/filer/oppdater
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "FYLL-INN-FIL-ID",
  "kategori": "Noter",
  "verk": "Messiah",
  "anledning": "Julekonsert 2024"
}

### Batch-oppdater filmetadata
POST {{base}}/api/filer/batch-oppdater
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "files": [
    { "id": "FIL-ID-1", "kategori": "Noter", "verk": "Messiah" },
    { "id": "FIL-ID-2", "kategori": "Lyd", "verk": "Messiah" }
  ]
}

### Last opp fil (base64)
POST {{base}}/api/filer/last-opp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "test-fil.pdf",
  "contentType": "application/pdf",
  "base64": "JVBERi0xLjQK",
  "kategori": "Noter",
  "verk": "Test"
}

### ===========================
### BLOB
### ===========================

### Last opp til blob (fra URL)
POST {{base}}/api/blob/last-opp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "files": [
    {
      "sourceUrl": "https://example.com/file.pdf",
      "blobName": "sanger/file.pdf"
    }
  ]
}

### Tom blob-storage
POST {{base}}/api/blob/tom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": true
}
